channel.title: How do you add a model? (317)
channel.description: just wondering how to add a model to your server for example, new d scim look or new whip look etc. i have a 317 server. if you don't know how can you atleast post a link to a tutorial? thanks ;D

item.title: How do you add a model? (317)
item.dc:creator: @marcbob marcbob
item.description:
@marcbob wrote:

Paste the model into your model folder in your client.

Then add the inits into class8 in your client.

Compile

Run your server and client and go in game and type “add model MODELID”
and where MODELID is you put the model number

after you added all the models ingame try spawning the item you tried to add.
IM not very good with explaining stuff but I hope you can kinda get it

And ya this is client help but w/e
